rows.label: tlk41700161_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I hear the Divine Beast Liberalitas
is somewhere in the Cloud Sea,
but I've never seen it.

rows.label: tlk41700161_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I thought I might be able to see it
if I went through the Cloudway, so
I went to Lud Cloudway, but...

rows.label: tlk41700161_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I just kept getting attacked by
ridiculously strong monsters, and I
couldn't see a trace of the Divine Beast.

rows.label: tlk41700161_02_msg0004
rows.name:
If you happen to see it... I want to
see it with my own eyes, so you don't
have to tell me what it was like.
